Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.23,0:02:09.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Vermilion juice
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.73,0:02:11.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Spoiling the end
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.36,0:02:14.65,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Performance of a predestined event
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.65,0:02:20.49,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Written by their thirst for destruction
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.07,0:02:23.45,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Day and night
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:26.62,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}We searched along the rails
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.62,0:02:29.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Hoping to find another trail
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.92,0:02:31.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Leading to heaven
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.42,0:02:34.00,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}The heavens are waiting for motion
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.00,0:02:36.71,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Fired up for action
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.71,0:02:37.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}There's no gain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.84,0:02:38.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:39.42,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.42,0:02:40.13,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:40.88,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Only pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.88,0:02:41.72,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}All this pain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.72,0:02:43.89,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}My pains don't exist to entertain
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.89,0:02:46.31,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Count with me, one two three
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:49.73,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many liters can you bleed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.14,0:02:53.52,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many turns you plan to last?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.52,0:02:56.07,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}How many lives you need?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:58.36,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I saw a star
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.36,0:03:01.57,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Brightening up the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.82,0:03:10.41,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}So don't you stop my fires from burning our everything
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:15.29,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}You and me are nothing but temporary
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.29,0:03:20.59,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Don't you start begging for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.59,0:03:22.09,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}For when I win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.09,0:03:23.84,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}I won't forgive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:25.39,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:26.93,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}And I shall win
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:33.69,OPJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}Yes, I shall win your one-sided game
